          "content_hash": "ff7d124612cd9b53",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "JHU Daniel Khashabi （听说给黑推）"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "0000000000000000",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": ""
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "c8ede421ca1224b4",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "Columbia University - Sharon Di"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "b0c68deeaa336e93",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "全校范围招几十个MS进组科研养蛊 最后蛊王可以留phd"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "d362386a7b30295e",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "非常push，组里都是牛马，周末和晚上开会是常态，假期也开会"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "0000000000000000",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": ""
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "f2d60a6b8e12693a",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "Columbia Xiaodong Wang"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "b7b72130f82dc5d5",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "懂得都懂"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "9d9c0be14b72b142",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "学生被搞抑郁了"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "9fb6a975cf6bc8a1",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "外面接项目搞钱"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "0000000000000000",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": ""
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "6b3ca44c9f2da12e",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "UW-Madison Xiaobin Xiong"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "bf7bcad0ee2ff268",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "回国了，在上海创智"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "fa0dee765a14b525",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "自己从来没做过ai为了蹭管自己的lab叫legged AI lab"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "d97245919c060c1d",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "曾言CoRL是水会不许投"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "115185f0a9421148",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "回国导致自己phd居无定所"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "9a8b81d4e8cef30f",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "抽象，想一出是一出，idea像是在做梦，技术细节特别是learning依托"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "0000000000000000",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": ""
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "feeaae04f03aaf1e",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "UW-Madison Sikai Chen"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "b71719fd3f768f3b",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "上学的时候一堆造假paper"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "d66b9c1936d80410",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "把学生逼到腰出问题做手术，躺在床上养病，还push该学生写proposal"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "c38c94194ed4b178",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "逼迫学生凌晨送他去机场，去他家给他洗碗"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "7be6f721b50a9d59",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "不给学生买电脑，给他老婆买，开会不给学生报销，但给他老婆吃饭报销"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "1cfd004fcca0bb3f",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "做博后的时候让学生给他付房租"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "5b66eada70e6b23a",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "一开始看起来是个很友好的学长，但抢师弟一作，要求labmate和导师邮件必须cc他"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "83cd6468e29feb4f",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "请学生吃饭，让学生付钱"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "e95d5b06d7633f0b",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "他技术一窍不通。。。还喜欢微操"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "c7c0c1b88f9e8764",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "自称做AI的，指着无监督学习问学生“这是监督学习还是什么？我不清楚，你清楚么”"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "0000000000000000",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": ""
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "3ac735bc7756b120",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "UW-Madison Junjie Hu"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "3da002abc4514d26",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": " 鱼王，前一秒说好，后一秒直接玩消失，毫无时间观念"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "0000000000000000",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": ""
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "426f7130070da068",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "TAMU Zhiyuan Yu"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "6bfe416d5bd28be0",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "超级海王，据说一个申请季能养几十条鱼, 在已经有很多鱼的情况下还发招生贴"
        },
